00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:55,240
and inside the cover, it was full of the smoke from burning.

253
00:19:55,240 --> 00:20:00,280
And then the wine will absorb all the smoke from the burnt fruit wood.

254
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,560
Will this work?

255
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:04,060
Sure. Do you have a cover here?

256
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:05,150
There should be.

257
00:20:05,150 --> 00:20:08,030
Okay, then we'll try it. I brought ingredients.

258
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:32,000
Hurry and try it.

259
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:38,820
It works!

260
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:43,090
The smoke has indeed absorbed the fishy odor completely.

261
00:20:43,090 --> 00:20:44,860
The effect is better than I thought it would be.

262
00:20:44,860 --> 00:20:48,950
This way, the crayfish's fishy odor will be completely removed.

263
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:51,350
If this method works,

264
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:55,660
you should handle the beef the same way, just in case.

265
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:58,480
Okay. This way, the taste will be uniform.

266
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:01,290
It can also decrease the oily flavor. Good suggestion.

267
00:21:01,290 --> 00:21:03,810
But if we also add beef,

268
00:21:03,810 --> 00:21:06,580
this cover will be enough.

269
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,780
Not a problem.

270
00:21:07,780 --> 00:21:09,620
Yuxuan has a professional cold smoker.

271
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:11,480
As long as the smoke method works,

272
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,400
I can arrange for someone to do it.

273
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,310
It won't draw attention.

274
00:21:15,910 --> 00:21:17,420
Then that works.

275
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:19,050
Thank you.

276
00:21:19,050 --> 00:21:20,660
I know you made this.

277
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:22,650
I will give you credit for it.

278
00:21:23,290 --> 00:21:27,030
Don't be so polite. I'm not used to it.

279
00:21:27,990 --> 00:21:30,490
I'm doing this for Mr. Jiang.

280
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:35,150
If you say this, then we're even.

281
00:21:42,370 --> 00:21:44,040
Chef Mai, Chef Mai!

282
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:47,310
I'll do it. Just let me do it.

283
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:51,200
You only need to do a little bit. How can you do this work?

284
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:55,360
You say that, but if I don't do the work, will it be enough for Jiang Qianfan?

285
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:57,520
Isn't he something?

286
00:21:57,520 --> 00:22:01,490
Forget about his stinky temper. Everyone knows about it and we're used to it,

287
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:04,730
but his cooking tastes horrible now. Look at that apprentice.

288
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:06,050
What kind of act is she putting on?

289
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:08,740
Don't talk anymore. It's not good if Mr. Jiang hears it.

290
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:12,580
What am I? Look at the time. Boris is about to be here.

291
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:15,030
He will talk a lot more uglily than I did!

292
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:19,870
- Besides, if he's afraid of people talking, then don't cook such bad-tasting stuff.
 - Say that again!

293
00:22:24,910 --> 00:22:28,190
Sure. I'll say it again then.

294
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:32,140
Mr. Jiang, I've reported this problem more than once or twice.

295
00:22:32,140 --> 00:22:37,590
That dish of yours, Wagyu Sirloin and Red Crayfish, really has a big problem. First of all, the crayfish's fishy odor isn't removed.

296
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:39,570
Every customer who ate it found it unacceptable.

297
00:22:39,570 --> 00:22:43,090
Let me tell you. You are the first one who doesn't understand my cooking!

298
00:22:43,090 --> 00:22:46,840
- Chef Mai, don't talk anymore. Calm down.
- No, I'm saying what's right. What am I afraid of?

299
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:52,580
I am definitely not the first one and won't be the last one. As it looks now, the entire chef team thinks the same way.

300
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:56,420
Da Mai, I'll say it again.

301
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:59,950
Yuxuan is Jiang Xianfan's restaurant. Jiang Xianfan is the standard.

302
00:22:59,950 --> 00:23:02,830
Elise, no need to say it anymore!

303
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:07,570
Sure. Everyone heard it too. Mr. Jiang is the standard.

304
00:23:07,570 --> 00:23:09,390
This is what they mean by, "What lowly people say count little."

305
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:12,710
It's useless for us little people to give any suggestion.

306
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:16,350
Boris should be here soon. I sure would like to see what he'll say.

307
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:19,590
Fine. Just you wait!

308
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:21,530
What are you looking at? Get to work!

309
00:23:21,530 --> 00:23:22,800
Forget it, forget it!

310
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:25,290
Elise, come inside!

311
00:23:28,290 --> 00:23:30,200
Da Mai has told you before?

312
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:32,350
- He has.
- Why didn't you tell me?

313
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:34,410
Once Boris has eaten and finished the livestream, it'll be too late.

314
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:37,810
Is it because you think I won't change even after telling me? Right?

315
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:40,140
Yes.

316
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:42,360
Fine. All of you are right.

317
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:45,500
I won't change it! Cook this dish my way!

318
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:18,330
Anyone watching my livestream today

319
00:24:18,330 --> 00:24:22,540
has really found treasure.

320
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:27,160
Boris's Michelin Blacklist is here again.

321
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:30,480
This place is Yuxuan in Shanghai.

322
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,330
I've been here before,

323
00:24:33,330 --> 00:24:36,160
but I also said,

324
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:39,800
I'd come here again when the new seasonal dishes are out.

325
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:43,790
That's why I'm here today.

326
00:24:44,670 --> 00:24:49,510
Everyone has seen the first round of the Future Star Culinary Competition.

327
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:51,930
Jiang's achievement...

328
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:56,680
Did he have an achievement?

329
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:59,260
Somehow, I don't remember.

330
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:13,030
Mr. Jiang.

331
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:38,230
Xiao Yang!

332
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:50,780
What is this? Burnt Pu'er tea's stalks?

333
00:25:50,780 --> 00:25:54,250
This... Sorry, Mr. Jiang.

334
00:25:59,670 --> 00:26:01,240
Whose idea was this?

335
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,290
What idea?

336
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:07,870
You burnt the tea and used the smoking method to remove the fish odor from the beef and crayfish, right?

337
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:11,090
You are right. Sure enough, nothing escapes your eyes.

338
00:26:11,090 --> 00:26:12,290
It was Lin Kesong's idea.

339
00:26:12,290 --> 00:26:13,670
What do you mean?

340
00:26:13,670 --> 00:26:17,010
Lin Kesong called me and told me to go there for something important.

341
00:26:17,010 --> 00:26:21,090
She said the online reviews all said Wagyu Beef and Red Crayfish didn't taste good,

342
00:26:21,090 --> 00:26:23,390
so she thought of a way to improve it. If you don't believe, look here.

343
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:25,870
I don't want to look at it. Why did you listen to her?

344
00:26:25,870 --> 00:26:28,320
Because she showed you how to eat the crayfish.

345
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:31,030
She knows more and understands more.

346
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:34,870
Besides, you trust her, so I trust her too.

347
00:26:34,870 --> 00:26:36,300
We are doing it for your sake.

348
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:39,730
For my sake? Do you know what disgusts me the most?

349
00:26:43,630 --> 00:26:46,430
Great, Chef Jiang.

350
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:48,740
personally delivers the dish to me.

351
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:52,900
You want to help me get more fans? No.

352
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:55,280
You are afraid of me. Are you afraid of me?

353
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:58,060
I just want to see your satisfied expression in person.

354
00:26:58,060 --> 00:27:01,420
I'll consider what you say as a compliment to me.

355
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:04,790
Because Boris' dedication to food

356
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:08,030
is incomparable.

357
00:27:08,030 --> 00:27:12,040
My pickiness and ruthlessness on food

358
00:27:12,040 --> 00:27:14,810
is also incomparable.

359
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:32,600
Is there any way of escape?

360
00:27:33,330 --> 00:27:35,170
No way.

361
00:27:35,170 --> 00:27:38,280
Have you been bewitched lately?

362
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:42,740
"Meeting of Two Seasons" really tastes terrible.

363
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:46,770
Red crayfish and steak. The idea sounds good,

364
00:27:46,770 --> 00:27:49,730
but when I eat it,

365
00:27:49,730 --> 00:27:55,010
the inner fishy odor of the crayfish isn't removed at all.

366
00:27:55,010 --> 00:27:57,830
Adding that with the fat from the Wagyu beef,

367
00:27:57,830 --> 00:28:01,690
it's like putting a hydrogen bomb on the tip of the tongue.

368
00:28:01,690 --> 00:28:05,870
Jiang, can you really not tell how bad it tastes?

369
00:28:05,870 --> 00:28:09,900
What a joke. I think there is only one reason that you don't like it.

370
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:12,450
You have too much fat in your body.

371
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:19,700
If it doesn't taste good, you only blame other people, so I can only eat it if I lose weight?

372
00:28:20,650 --> 00:28:23,600
Jiang, you got a zero in the competition,

373
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:27,950
but you are still so arrogant. Don't you feel embarrassed?

374
00:28:28,810 --> 00:28:33,810
Don't you think this is the best way to get attention? Enjoy it slowly.

375
00:28:44,390 --> 00:28:45,970
Let me tell you all.

376
00:28:45,970 --> 00:28:49,660
This dish really tastes awful.

377
00:28:49,660 --> 00:28:52,630
He has disappointed me too much.

378
00:28:53,290 --> 00:28:57,900
Yuxuan restaurant... Garbage!

379
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:05,770
[Jiang Qianfan]

380
00:29:06,800 --> 00:29:11,040
Lin Kesong, come to Yuxuan. Now!

381
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:13,530
What is this?

382
00:29:20,090 --> 00:29:23,900
Please come again. Goodbye.

383
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:27,070
Miss Lin? Why are you here?

384
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:33,250
- Mr. Jiang told me to come.
- Mr. Jiang is in a bad mood today. Be careful.

385
00:29:34,840 --> 00:29:37,490
I'm going in then.

386
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:49,820
Mr. Jiang, I'm here.

387
00:29:51,580 --> 00:29:55,260
Lin Kesong, how long have I been teaching you?

388
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:57,320
About a month?

389
00:29:57,320 --> 00:29:59,730
Exactly how long?

390
00:29:59,730 --> 00:30:02,200
Isn't a month about 30—

391
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:04,560
No need to count!

392
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:08,440
Therefore, you are awesome now and don't need to learn from me anymore!

393
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:10,400
What do you mean?

394
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:15,840
What do I mean? You are so awesome that you can change my dish!

395
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:23,970
Anyone who doesn't understand my food is stupid! Whoever changes my dishes is an enemy!

396
00:30:23,970 --> 00:30:26,850
You are awesome. Right now,

397
00:30:26,850 --> 00:30:31,540
you clean up the front, back kitchen, fresh produce handling room, and the restroom!

398
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:34,050
Xiao Pa!

399
00:30:34,050 --> 00:30:37,720
You are in charge of monitoring! Everyone else can leave!

400
00:30:54,590 --> 00:30:56,710
Why didn't you explain it clearly to Mr. Jiang?

401
00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:59,650
Sorry, Miss Lin. I did explain.

402
00:30:59,650 --> 00:31:02,160
You better do what Oliver says.

403
00:31:03,790 --> 00:31:08,360
Yuxuan is large. I advise you to start right away.

404
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:40,230
♫  I just wait for this moment  ♫

