00:31:42,780 --> 00:31:44,930
♫  Feel the air  ♫

406
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:46,850
Why are you here?

407
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:50,540
I've been here for a while.

408
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:54,460
I watched you for a long time. Oliver, don't drink anymore.

409
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:57,120
You are drinking too much.

410
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:04,520
♫  I tell myself there is nothing bad  ♫

411
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:07,860
♫  Falling  ♫

412
00:32:07,860 --> 00:32:11,690
Am I being ludicrous?

413
00:32:11,690 --> 00:32:13,170
I...

