00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,980
♫  Seeing  ♫

415
00:32:15,980 --> 00:32:16,940
Jiang Qianfan...

416
00:32:16,940 --> 00:32:19,650
♫  Something happen  ♫

417
00:32:19,650 --> 00:32:21,900
Michelin three-star chef...

418
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:25,370
♫  How can  ♫

419
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:27,610
Has lost the sense of taste.

420
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:35,900
♫  You said, don't be afraid  ♫

421
00:32:36,970 --> 00:32:38,920
Am I doomed?

422
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:42,550
Of course not. You still have me.

423
00:32:43,350 --> 00:32:45,310
I like eating.

424
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,650
Thank you.

425
00:32:53,140 --> 00:32:55,450
Even now, you are still consoling me.

426
00:32:56,810 --> 00:32:59,010
But I know it myself.

427
00:33:01,130 --> 00:33:03,940
If Michelin's secret scout has already visited,

428
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:08,740
then everything will be ruined.

429
00:33:12,250 --> 00:33:13,930
Oliver,

430
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:17,960
I've said it many times. Michelin isn't important to me.

431
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:21,010
You don't have to be sorry to me.

432
00:33:21,010 --> 00:33:26,110
No matter what, I'm happy to be with you. Even if the entire world is on the other side, I will stay by you.

433
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,990
Why?

434
00:33:33,140 --> 00:33:35,930
Why are you still so good to me?

435
00:33:35,930 --> 00:33:37,550
Because...

436
00:33:38,430 --> 00:33:41,370
This is how I am, Oliver.

437
00:33:51,850 --> 00:33:53,950
I know that

438
00:33:59,030 --> 00:34:01,700
I am a pretty unlikable person.

439
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:05,590
I've made it where no one likes me.

440
00:34:06,210 --> 00:34:08,240
Why are you still here?

441
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,520
What do you really want?

442
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:20,670
Forget it.

443
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:25,540
Let's not talk about these things today.

444
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:30,060
I don't want to go home early. Come,

445
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:31,880
let's drink together.

446
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:34,790
No, I can't drink. I don't want to make the same mistake as last time.

447
00:34:34,790 --> 00:34:36,330
Cheers.

448
00:34:45,950 --> 00:34:47,710
I'm so aggrieved.

449
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:51,210
In front of everyone in public, did he even consider my feelings?

450
00:34:51,210 --> 00:34:53,140
Do I want to lose face?

451
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:58,830
I almost shouted. If his sense of taste was fine, he would know why I had to make the change.

452
00:34:58,830 --> 00:35:01,960
Miss Lin, you should hurry and go back. I called a car for you, and it'll be here soon.

453
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,370
No need.

454
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:10,410
Mr. Jiang left a long time go and he won't come back. You should hurry and go back to rest.

455
00:35:12,390 --> 00:35:17,710
This is nothing. We're used to being scolded. Don't take it to heart.

456
00:35:36,890 --> 00:35:38,420
I want to go back.

457
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,790
Come.

458
00:35:40,980 --> 00:35:43,840
Careful. Take it easy.

459
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:48,060
Careful with the head. Careful with the head.

460
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:53,760
- Come drink!
- Thanks. Thank you.

461
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,820
Come for a drink.

462
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:12,240
I really can't persist anymore.

463
00:36:22,810 --> 00:36:26,660
He scolded his disciple in front of everyone today. What does he mean? Isn't it for us to hear?

464
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:29,030
- Thanks.
- Enjoy.

465
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:31,840
What kind of place is Yuxuan?

466
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:36,140
It's his territory. Will he let you get an upper hand?

467
00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:38,770
We have to be reasonable on everything, right?

468
00:36:38,770 --> 00:36:41,530
Am I wrong when I criticize Jiang Qianfan?

469
00:36:41,530 --> 00:36:46,320
Didn't I guess it right? Later on, Boris said even worse and it was livestreamed. Isn't it embarrassing?

470
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:49,220
He deserved it. All day long, he's so arrogant.

471
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:53,260
I've seen him in the restaurant. I said, "Hello," but he pretended not to hear.

472
00:36:53,260 --> 00:36:55,500
But on the other hand,

473
00:36:56,470 --> 00:37:00,530
when Boris did that, it's Yuxuan that got embarrassed.

474
00:37:01,680 --> 00:37:04,840
What? Do you really think of Yuxuan as your family?

475
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:10,650
How else? After all, I am Yuxuan's lead chef. If Yuxuan loses face, I lose face too.

476
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,440
Here.

477
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:15,820
Let me tell you this way.

478
00:37:15,820 --> 00:37:18,520
I'm already discussing with the next one.

479
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:23,560
You're good.

480
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:27,510
Aren't you the best actor? Not a trace at all.

481
00:37:27,510 --> 00:37:28,660
Which restaurant?

482
00:37:28,660 --> 00:37:30,490
Fuli. Do you know about it?

483
00:37:30,490 --> 00:37:32,470
Sure! An old restaurant.

484
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:37,290
They are recruiting now. How about it? The two of us can go there together.

485
00:37:37,290 --> 00:37:41,350
I'll chat with them. You'll definitely be the executive chef when you go there.

486
00:37:43,410 --> 00:37:45,580
Da Mai.

487
00:37:46,390 --> 00:37:48,800
Do you really think this incident with Jiang Qianfan is over?

488
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:51,590
He'll be humble tomorrow and apologize to you?

489
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:54,370
That's impossible. I've never seen any man being so broadminded.

490
00:37:54,370 --> 00:37:56,810
It's even more impossible for Jiang Qianfan?

491
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:00,560
He can do this to you today,

492
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:04,000
he can do it to the others tomorrow.

493
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:06,220
This doesn't sound good, but

494
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:09,410
there's no telling how long we can stay in Yuxuan.

495
00:38:12,010 --> 00:38:15,370
Enough now. No more talking! One more drink.

496
00:38:15,370 --> 00:38:17,260
Come.

497
00:38:35,530 --> 00:38:37,440
What's going on?

498
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:40,530
Lin Kesong, come help!

499
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:45,590
The steps.

500
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:49,140
Open the door.

501
00:38:57,010 --> 00:39:01,540
Don't leave me. I don't want to be alone.

502
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:07,570
Okay, Oliver. I won't leave. I'll stay here and not go anywhere.

