00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:43,450
Still feeling aggrieved?

505
00:39:43,450 --> 00:39:45,120
What do you think?

506
00:39:48,260 --> 00:39:52,940
Sorry, Lin Kesong. I'll apologize to you on his behalf.

507
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:55,630
So sorry, my dear.

508
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:59,220
Oliver is really like a devil sometimes.

509
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:02,440
He can make you feel like it's better to be dead than alive.

510
00:40:03,670 --> 00:40:05,480
I'll answer this call.

511
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:19,800
Not yet, Mom. He is in a bad mood today, so I couldn't say it.

512
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:24,510
When it's time to be ruthless, you are actually kind. You can't be this way.

513
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:26,800
Are you still with him now?

514
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:31,170
Yes, he's drunk. I just brought him back home.

515
00:40:33,050 --> 00:40:35,060
He won't let me leave.

516
00:40:35,810 --> 00:40:38,490
This is a great opportunity.

517
00:40:38,490 --> 00:40:43,420
While he is drunk, make him sign the contract, regardless of what trick you use.

518
00:40:43,420 --> 00:40:47,250
I don't believe he will deny it afterwards.

519
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:50,400
I'll wait for your good news.

520
00:41:08,470 --> 00:41:14,340
♫  You are the stranger I want to know  ♫

521
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:18,200
♫  Don't let me go  ♫

522
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:22,320
♫  I will do little tricks for you  ♫

523
00:41:23,350 --> 00:41:29,460
♫  Don't bury your secret heart  ♫

524
00:41:29,460 --> 00:41:31,530
♫  Show them who you are  ♫

525
00:41:31,530 --> 00:41:36,700
♫  We sing a song for love  ♫

526
00:41:37,620 --> 00:41:43,340
♫ Listen to your heart, to your heart  ♫
